title: Ep. - 349 - MARGARET JOSEPHS FROM REAL HOUSEWIVES OF NEW JERSEY
description:
Margaret Josephs from Bravo’s Real Housewives of New Jersey is the author of Caviar Dreams, Tuna Fish Budget. She talks to Kate about her childhood “raised by wolves,” her divorce, finding love with her contractor, building her businesses, and becoming a television personality at age 49.
